{"tid":984590,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"德國設法阻止華為競投5G網絡合約","createTime":"2019-01-17T02:33:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-20T02:52:04.000Z","uid":147314,"like":51,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"283cba8f23d9ee41a9d6a74c5c14526801702e52","tid":984590,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T02:33:48.000Z","msg":"德國報章報道，當地政府積極考慮定出嚴格的保安要求，以及透過其他方法，務求排除中國電訊設備製造商華為，競投德國的5G網絡合約。美國早前接觸盟國，指華為可能帶來網絡安全風險。華為批評指控並無根據。德國政府去年底表示，並無法律基礎，排除任何公司競投5G合約。但報道引述德國政府消息人士說，當局正研究定出一些華為無法達到的安全標準，甚至修訂電訊條例，作為排除華為競投德國5G合約的最後一著。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?csid=261_341&amp;itemid=1057795\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3Fcsid%3D261_341%26itemid%3D1057795&d=ENjt5TdXBxjpftf5WjULUC7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=c21e37e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?csid=261_341&amp;itemid=1057795</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85b7ace9e96e91ef4758bf3e08caf2b81a64030f","tid":984590,"uid":147314,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T02:34:50.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Germany considering ways to exclude Huawei from 5G auction: report</span></strong><br />\n<br />\nBERLIN (Reuters) - The German government is actively considering stricter security requirements and other ways to exclude China&rsquo;s Huawei Technologies [HWT.UL] from a buildout of fifth-generation (5G) mobile networks, the Handelsblatt newspaper reported.<br />\n<br />\nHandelsblatt, citing government sources, said government officials were discussing setting security standards that Huawei could not achieve, effectively blocking its participation. Changes to the German telecommunications law were also under consideration as a last resort, the paper said.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reuters.com/article/us-germany-china-huawei/germany-considering-ways-to-exclude-huawei-from-5g-auction-report-idUSKCN1PA32B\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fus-germany-china-huawei%2Fgermany-considering-ways-to-exclude-huawei-from-5g-auction-report-idUSKCN1PA32B&d=ENjt5TdXBxjpftf5WjULUC7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=f92cf6c2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fus-germany-china-huawei%2Fgermany-considering-ways-to-exclude-huawei-from-5g-auction-report-idUSKCN1PA32B&h=2dc973c0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reuters.com/article/us-germany-china-huawei/germany-considering-ways-to-exclude-huawei-from-5g-auction-report-idUSKCN1PA32B</a>"},{"pid":"e98de470561d714a22c75d5f00f5eec3b42c8c0d","tid":984590,"uid":107364,"like":3,"dislike":46,"score":-43,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T02:36:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"905cf9299c8ebc599aa5f6fea49e138aab7245b2","tid":984590,"uid":147314,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T02:44:53.000Z","msg":"支支無資格講自由市場<br />\n唔止鬼佬，日本、台灣，好快成個文明世界都會封你 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67dfecbbccfa0c5bfc81a92d2979d012af6a3e19","tid":984590,"uid":137217,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T02:45:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://today.line.me/HK/pc/article/%E6%9C%9B%E9%80%80%E5%87%BA%E5%85%B1%E7%94%A2%E9%BB%A8%E3%80%80%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E8%91%97%E5%90%8D%E5%AD%B8%E8%80%85%E8%8C%85%E4%BA%8E%E8%BB%BE%EF%BC%9A%E6%88%91%E4%B8%8D%E4%BA%A4%E9%BB%A8%E8%B2%BB%EF%BC%8C%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E6%8A%8A%E6%88%91%E9%96%8B%E9%99%A4%E4%BA%86%E5%90%A7-BwrBeQ?utm_source=fbshare\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftoday.line.me%2FHK%2Fpc%2Farticle%2F%25E6%259C%259B%25E9%2580%2580%25E5%2587%25BA%25E5%2585%25B1%25E7%2594%25A2%25E9%25BB%25A8%25E3%2580%2580%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E8%2591%2597%25E5%2590%258D%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E8%2580%2585%25E8%258